(12236, 480, 'blog_title', 'Creating a sustainable Supply Chain Framework through smart sourcing'),
(12237, 480, '_blog_title', 'field_66dbf3968cff0'),
(12238, 480, 'blog_content', 'Creating a sustainable supply chain is a pressing concern for businesses across all industries. \r\nWith increasing consumer demand for environmentally friendly and socially responsible products, \r\ncompanies are under pressure to source their materials and products in a sustainable manner.'),
(12239, 480, '_blog_content', 'field_66dbf39e8cff1'),
(12240, 480, 'blog_content2', 'Additionally, getting familiar with popular frameworks like React,\r\n            Vue, or Angular will significantly improve your development\r\n            workflow. Frameworks make it easier to create complex applications\r\n            by providing structure and best practices right out of the box.\r\n          </br>\r\n            To cap it all off, always strive to build projects. Real-world\r\n            projects not only sharpen your skills but also provide something\r\n            tangible to show to potential employers.'),
(12241, 480, '_blog_content2', 'field_66dfeaead548c'),
