(12562, 655, 'about_mission_sections_3_section_description', 'Our values form the foundational cornerstones on which the superstructure of Acceleron has been built.\r\nThe Value framework of Customer Centricity, Professional and Personal caring of the employees, Collaboration amongst Acceleron citizens, Entrepreneurial orientation of its members, and demonstration of Excellence in all its actions drive Acceleron towards achieving a sustainable competitive advantage and market leadership in this ever-dynamic business environment'),
