(13183, 651, '_blog_title', 'field_66dbf3968cff0'),
(13184, 651, 'blog_content', 'Creating a sustainable supply chain is a pressing concern for businesses across all industries. \r\nWith increasing consumer demand for environmentally friendly and socially responsible products, \r\ncompanies are under pressure to source their materials and products in a sustainable manner.'),
(13185, 651, '_blog_content', 'field_66dbf39e8cff1'),
(13186, 651, 'blog_content2', 'One strategy that businesses can adopt to achieve this is smart sourcing. By implementing smart sourcing practices, companies can not only reduce their environmental footprint but also create a more resilient and efficient supply chain. This article explores the concept of smart sourcing and its benefits, as well as provides practical tips for implementing it in your organization.'),
