(13213, 653, '_blog_title', 'field_66dbf3968cff0'),
(13214, 653, 'blog_content', 'In an era of rapid technological advancements, the mining industry is lagging behind in adopting digital transformation. Traditional mining operations are often plagued by inefficiencies, safety concerns, and lack of collaboration.'),
