(13575, 660, 'about_mission_sections_0_section_description', 'Design, Manufacture, Market and Maintain best-in-class equipment for various key sectors including infrastructure, energy, mining and defence for domestic and global markets.\r\nAttain consistent business growth and maintain market leadership through engaged & capable employees and products of global standards, while maintaining highest level of commitment to organizational values and ethics'),
