(13587, 660, 'about_mission_sections_2_section_description', 'Acceleron Solutions is a part of the 75 year old Gainwell Group, a diversified conglomerate, headquartered in Kolkata India, and having branches and subsidiaries across India, USA Australia, Singapore, Nepal, and Bhutan.'),
